Method Detail

withUriValidation

ModelBuilder.DefaultUriSettings withUriValidation()
Declares that the model to be created will validate URIs given as input according to RFC 2396. This is the default option.

Returns:
an object to handle the rest of the procedure of the model creation

withoutUriValidation

ModelBuilder.DefaultUriSettings withoutUriValidation()
Declares that the model to be created will not validate URIs. This does not turn off validation during parsing, but only validation during creation of the model through the API (methods Model.mapResource()).

Returns:
an object to handle the rest of the procedure of the model creation
